        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer627492732" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer211699492951422170">I bought this free from amazon, and I have to say it is really good. I couldn&apos;t believe it was self published. It always amazes me what publishing houses chose to pass on. The plot is unique and fresh, the characters well developed. It is set up as a trilogy, so I hope upon reading the other books I find out more about Sonnett and Rose. It takes time travel and turns it on its ear a bit. Tp notch. Check it out.</span>
  <span id="freeText211699492951422170" style="display:none">I bought this free from amazon, and I have to say it is really good. I couldn't believe it was self published. It always amazes me what publishing houses chose to pass on. The plot is unique and fresh, the characters well developed. It is set up as a trilogy, so I hope upon reading the other books I find out more about Sonnett and Rose. It takes time travel and turns it on its ear a bit. Tp notch. Check it out.</span>
